Package: ggpcp
Type: Package
Title: Parallel Coordinate Plots in the 'ggplot2' Framework
Version: 0.2.0
Date: 2022-11-22
Authors@R: c(
    person("Heike", "Hofmann", , "hofmann@iastate.edu",
